\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 Overview\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 The AI Agents: Intensive Vibe Coding Capstone Project invites participants to build an AI agent using the concepts, tools, and best practices learned in {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.kaggle.com/competitions/5-day-ai-agents-intensive-vibecoding-course-with-google/overview"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 Kaggle\'92s 5-Day AI Agents: Intensive Vibe Coding Course}} with Google. Participants will create a practical, real-world solution that demonstrates how AI agents can automate tasks, assist users, solve business challenges, or improve everyday workflows.\
Submissions should showcase both the project's value and technical implementation through a Kaggle Writeup, public codebase, video demonstration, and project link. Projects may be entered into one of four tracks: Agents for Good, Agents for Business, Concierge Agents, or Freestyle and will be evaluated based on innovation, solution design, communication, and the effective application of course concepts and agent technologies.\
