\pard\pardeftab720\sa319\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf0 c. Public Project Link\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf0 A URL to your working product or interactive demo. This allows judges to experience your project firsthand, if applicable. It should be publicly accessible and not require a login or paywall. If a live demo is not feasible, a link to your public code repository (e.g., GitHub) is required, including detailed setup instructions.\
